# SaaS Inventory Management System - Project Summary

## üéØ Project Overview
A comprehensive, enterprise-grade SaaS inventory management system designed for small retail businesses managing 1,000-5,000 products. Built with multi-tenant architecture, role-based access control, and a 3-tier subscription model.

## üèóÔ∏è Architecture
- **Backend**: Node.js with Express.js framework
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Knex.js ORM
- **Authentication**: JWT with bcrypt password hashing
- **Payment Processing**: Stripe integration
- **Security**: Rate limiting, Helmet.js, CORS, input validation
- **Logging**: Winston.js for comprehensive logging

## üóÑÔ∏è Database Schema
### Core Tables:
- **organizations**: Multi-tenant SaaS structure
- **users**: User management with role-based access (admin, manager, staff, viewer)
- **products**: Product catalog with SKU, pricing, stock levels
- **categories**: Hierarchical product categorization
- **suppliers**: Supplier/vendor management
- **inventory_transactions**: Complete stock movement tracking
- **purchase_orders**: Purchase order management
- **purchase_order_items**: Line items for purchase orders
- **purchase_receipts**: Goods receipt tracking
- **notification_preferences**: User notification settings
- **api_usage_logs**: Subscription usage tracking

## üöÄ Key Features Implemented

### 1. Authentication & Authorization
- JWT-based authentication with secure token management
- Role-based access control (Admin, Manager, Staff, Viewer)
- Organization-based multi-tenancy
- Password reset functionality
- User profile management

### 2. Product Management
- Complete CRUD operations for products
- SKU and barcode management
- Pricing management (cost/selling price)
- Stock level configuration (min/max/reorder points)
- Category assignment and hierarchy
- Bulk import/export functionality (CSV)
- Custom fields and metadata support

### 3. Inventory Management
- Real-time stock tracking with transaction history
- Multiple transaction types (purchase, sale, adjustment, transfer, return, damaged)
- Stock level validation and negative stock prevention
- Automatic stock level updates on goods receipt
- Low stock alerts with severity prioritization
- Current stock level calculations
- Bulk stock adjustment capabilities

### 4. Supplier Management
- Supplier information management
- Payment terms configuration
- Supplier-product relationships
- Supplier statistics and performance tracking
- Purchase order integration

### 5. Purchase Order System
- Complete purchase order lifecycle management
- Order status tracking (draft ‚Üí sent ‚Üí confirmed ‚Üí received)
- Goods receipt processing with partial receipts
- Automatic inventory updates on receipt
- Purchase order number generation
- Supplier integration with delivery tracking

### 6. Analytics & Reporting
- Dashboard overview with key metrics
- Inventory value reports by category
- Stock movement analysis (daily/weekly/monthly)
- Low stock reports with reorder recommendations
- Purchase order tracking and analysis
- Real-time alerts and notifications

### 7. Subscription & Payment System
- 3-tier subscription model (Free, Basic, Professional, Enterprise)
- Stripe integration for payment processing
- Subscription upgrade/downgrade functionality
- Usage tracking and limit enforcement
- Webhook handling for payment events
- Trial period management

### 8. Security Implementation
- Rate limiting to prevent API abuse
- Input validation with express-validator
- SQL injection prevention with Knex.js
- CORS configuration for secure cross-origin requests
- Helmet.js for security headers
- Password hashing with bcrypt (12 salt rounds)
- Environment variable protection

## üìä Subscription Tiers

### Free Tier
- 100 products max
- 2 users max
- 10 suppliers max
- 1GB storage
- 1,000 API calls/month

### Basic Tier ($29/month)
- 1,000 products max
- 5 users max
- 50 suppliers max
- 5GB storage
- 10,000 API calls/month
- Basic reporting

### Professional Tier ($79/month)
- 5,000 products max
- 15 users max
- 200 suppliers max
- 25GB storage
- 50,000 API calls/month
- Advanced reporting and analytics

### Enterprise Tier ($199/month)
- Unlimited products/users/suppliers
- 100GB storage
- Unlimited API calls
- Priority support
- Advanced features

## üîß API Endpoints

### Authentication
- `POST /api/auth/register` - Organization and admin registration
- `POST /api/auth/login` - User login
- `GET /api/auth/profile` - Get current user profile
- `PUT /api/auth/profile` - Update user profile
- `PUT /api/auth/change-password` - Change password

### Products
- `GET /api/products` - List products with filtering/pagination
- `GET /api/products/:id` - Get single product details
- `POST /api/products` - Create new product
- `PUT /api/products/:id` - Update product
- `DELETE /api/products/:id` - Delete product
- `POST /api/products/bulk-import` - Bulk import products
- `GET /api/products/export/csv` - Export products to CSV

### Inventory
- `GET /api/inventory/transactions` - List inventory transactions
- `POST /api/inventory/transactions` - Create inventory transaction
- `GET /api/inventory/low-stock` - Get low stock alerts
- `GET /api/inventory/stock-levels` - Get current stock levels
- `POST /api/inventory/bulk-adjustment` - Bulk stock adjustment

### Suppliers
- `GET /api/suppliers` - List suppliers
- `GET /api/suppliers/:id` - Get supplier details
- `POST /api/suppliers` - Create supplier
- `PUT /api/suppliers/:id` - Update supplier
- `DELETE /api/suppliers/:id` - Delete supplier
- `GET /api/suppliers/:id/products` - Get supplier products

### Purchase Orders
- `GET /api/purchase-orders` - List purchase orders
- `GET /api/purchase-orders/:id` - Get purchase order details
- `POST /api/purchase-orders` - Create purchase order
- `PATCH /api/purchase-orders/:id/status` - Update order status
- `POST /api/purchase-orders/:id/receive` - Record goods receipt

### Analytics & Reports
- `GET /api/reports/dashboard` - Dashboard overview
- `GET /api/reports/inventory-value` - Inventory value report
- `GET /api/reports/stock-movements` - Stock movement analysis
- `GET /api/reports/low-stock` - Low stock report
- `GET /api/reports/purchase-orders` - Purchase order report

### Subscriptions
- `GET /api/subscription/plans` - Get subscription plans
- `GET /api/subscription/current` - Get current subscription
- `POST /api/subscription/checkout` - Create Stripe checkout
- `POST /api/subscription/cancel` - Cancel subscription
- `POST /api/subscription/update-plan` - Update plan
- `GET /api/subscription/usage` - Get usage statistics

## üõ°Ô∏è Security Features
- Rate limiting (100 requests per 15 minutes)
- Input validation and sanitization
- SQL injection prevention
- CORS protection
